title: Sawbones: Yes, More Medical Questions Answered!
description:
Does medicated chap stick doing anything? What are doctors hiding? Why can't you keep your bones? This week on Sawbones, Dr. Sydnee and Justin bring you answers to these questions and many more on a new Q&A episode!

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
